      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s high-revving masterpiece. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a crisp ZF 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing variable M differential lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and updated bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. While showing light patina consistent with a well-loved driver, its performance envelope remains sharp, offering the precise turn-in and balanced weight distribution defined by its MacPherson strut and multi-link suspension geometry.",
